Aaron, one thing you may want to try..If you are using something without a GUI, you could take a one or two day subscription to betange (£1) log into the same account and literally sit and watch (record) the ladders and see where your bets are being placed. Is the strat still doing EXACTLY what it was previously? Ive found that a visual interpretation can often give a different perspective and insight that just numbers alone.
(Good luck solving; been there too)
